# Mountain / Alpine theme
# Derived from a teal-sky snowcapped-peaks wallpaper
# Source with:  source ~/Projects/MyBar/themes/mountain.env && qs -p ~/Projects/MyBar/
# Or set AETHERA_THEME=mountain in your autostart.

